Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.46,0:19:52.11,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なんでなんで
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.11,0:19:53.37,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ちょっともう一回
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.52,0:19:55.95,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なんで
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.95,0:19:57.17,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,もう一回
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.32,0:19:59.42,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ああ　もう
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.22,0:20:03.39,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なんだこれ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.39,0:20:06.52,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,帽子で戻れるんじゃないの　違うの
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.52,0:20:07.93,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,って　ちょっと
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.81,0:20:09.56,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,そう
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.46,0:20:11.93,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,くれぐれも気をつけるんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.31,0:20:13.77,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ありがとう　お母さん
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.31,0:20:15.19,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,行ってきます
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.65,0:20:17.73,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,もし生きてる貂熊がいたら
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.08,0:20:21.28,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,バカなことやってないで　とっとと帰ってこいって伝えてね
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.52,0:20:22.20,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,分かった
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.57,0:20:24.08,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,必ずお父さんに伝える
