Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.49,0:20:26.18,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.18,0:20:27.17,JP-Main-Down-2,Iguchi,0,0,0,,久賀玲実
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.17,0:20:27.80,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.80,0:20:29.25,JP-Main-Down-2,Iguchi,0,0,0,,東雲晶
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.25,0:20:29.88,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.88,0:20:32.45,JP-Main-Down-2,Iguchi,0,0,0,,中富葉香　は休学中で
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.45,0:20:33.76,JP-Main-Down-2,Iguchi,0,0,0,,千倉静留
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.76,0:20:36.19,JP-Main-Down-2,Iguchi,0,0,0,,またしずるは休みか
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.19,0:20:38.50,JP-Main-Down-2,Iguchi,0,0,0,,三人とも静留がどうしたか知らないか
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.50,0:20:42.89,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,おとと夕方すれ違った時は　帽子の謎が解けたって
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.89,0:20:45.77,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,吾野の塾前を　ぼっちさんと走ってましたけど
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.77,0:20:46.70,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,何の謎
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.70,0:20:48.76,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,つか学校サボって何してんだろ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.76,0:20:49.51,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,不良
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.51,0:20:51.22,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留ちゃん不良になっちゃうの
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.22,0:20:53.94,JP-Main-Down-2,Iguchi,0,0,0,,不良行為をするような環境もないんで
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.94,0:20:56.14,JP-Main-Down-2,Iguchi,0,0,0,,そこは安心だと思うが
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.15,0:21:00.74,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,井口先生　お世話になりました
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.74,0:21:01.93,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,学校やります
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.93,0:21:02.90,JP-Main-Down-2,Group,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.02,0:21:05.38,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,よしよしよし
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.38,0:21:07.29,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,よしよしよしよし
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.29,0:21:08.25,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,よし
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.25,0:21:11.24,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,私はわけあって同乗できないが　これならなんとかなるだろう
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.24,0:21:14.65,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,7G崩壊のこの世界をその目で確かめてくれ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.65,0:21:16.47,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,報告を心待ちにしている
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.47,0:21:19.06,JP-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,いいか　生き残るために最も重要なの
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.66,0:21:22.66,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なあ　また中途半端なところで
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.66,0:21:23.95,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ん　でもまあいいや
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.95,0:21:24.88,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,だいたい分かったし
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.88,0:21:25.63,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,良くない
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.63,0:21:26.42,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,良くないでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.81,0:21:26.58,JP-Main-up-8-2,Akira,0,0,0,,良くない
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.58,0:21:27.59,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,え　びっくりした
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.59,0:21:29.94,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,もびっくりしたじゃないよ　静留ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.94,0:21:31.35,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,学校やめるって何
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.35,0:21:32.25,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ん
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.25,0:21:33.41,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,あとよろしく
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.41,0:21:34.34,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ちょっと行ってくる
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.34,0:21:35.23,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,え　どこへ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.52,0:21:37.30,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,池袋
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.32,0:21:39.54,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,え　まじで
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.54,0:21:40.64,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,そんないきなり
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.64,0:21:42.14,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,いきなりじゃないよ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.14,0:21:43.50,JP-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ちゃんと準備した
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.31,0:21:48.92,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,わ　動いてる
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.34,0:21:50.73,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,ちょっと待て　行く
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.73,0:21:51.86,JP-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,私も行く
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.86,0:21:52.57,JP-Main-Down-2,Group,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.57,0:21:53.24,JP-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,って　ま
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.24,0:21:55.43,JP-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,まじ　ちょ　噓
Comment: 0,0:00:26.60,0:00:28.60,ZH-Main-Down-2,,0,0,0,,OP前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.60,0:00:31.57,ZH-Main-Down-2,Group,0,0,0,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.27,0:00:45.55,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,欢迎来到7G网络启动纪念仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.73,0:00:49.17,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你可是第七万七千七百七十七位顾客
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.17,0:00:50.07,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,请问您怎么称呼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.07,0:00:50.91,ZH-Main-Down-2,Yoka,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.91,0:00:52.23,ZH-Main-Down-2,Yoka,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.09,0:00:55.58,ZH-Main-Down-2,Yoka,0,0,0,,我叫中富葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:00:57.45,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,欢迎您 葉香小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:01:02.02,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,我是全球7G传播委员会 会长芃伊斯·庞太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.02,0:01:06.96,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,葉香小姐对能够以超级速度连接世界的7G网络有什么期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.86,0:01:10.57,ZH-Main-Down-2,Yoka,0,0,0,,期待
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.57,0:01:11.00,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.62,0:01:14.24,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,无论何地 无论何人 都能即时交流 瞬间接触
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:16.80,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,这就是梦想中的新技术 7G网络
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.80,0:01:18.69,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,我们没赶上5G的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.69,0:01:20.64,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,而6G却大器晚成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.64,0:01:23.51,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,但是 我们终于用7G夺回日本国的荣誉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.51,0:01:25.98,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,虽然还是有些人反对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.98,0:01:27.14,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,甚至招来黑粉诽谤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.14,0:01:30.73,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,但是面对他们新闻学学的 我们没有退缩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:34.90,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,世界最先进的技术 全部都包含在7G里面 无限量投入
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:38.01,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,大脑所思想的 直接能够读取 全部主意都能处理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.01,0:01:40.62,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,想法马上传达 思考立刻行动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.62,0:01:43.69,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,好比神明力量使用者 就是所谓的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.69,0:01:45.31,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,7G
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.32,0:01:46.62,ZH-Main-up-8-2,Yoka,0,0,0,,那个 我能回家了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.76,0:01:48.98,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,那么接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.98,0:01:50.90,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,就请大家一同迎接
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.90,0:01:52.68,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,通往未来的世界历史时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.45,0:01:54.07,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,五
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.93,0:01:55.58,ZH-Main-Down-2,Group,0,0,0,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.31,0:01:57.09,ZH-Main-Down-2,Group,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.89,0:01:58.60,ZH-Main-Down-2,Group,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.44,0:02:00.33,ZH-Main-Down-2,Group,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.96,0:02:02.39,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,启动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.77,0:02:05.47,ZH-Main-Down-2,Group,0,0,0,,未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.43,0:02:09.89,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,未来启动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:41.13,ZH-Main-Down-2,Pontaro,0,0,0,,这是什么鬼啊
Comment: 0,0:02:41.40,0:02:43.40,ZH-Main-Down-2,,0,0,0,,正文
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:18.19,ZH-Main-up-8-2,Iguchi,0,0,0,,静留
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:22.57,ZH-Main-Down-2,Iguchi,0,0,0,,你未来到底想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:26.31,ZH-Main-Down-2,Iguchi,0,0,0,,这些荒谬的回答 你真觉得我会接受吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:29.03,ZH-Main-Down-2,Iguchi,0,0,0,,再说了 都已经过去两年了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:31.83,ZH-Main-Down-2,Iguchi,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:36.05,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,这里是 吾野站到达广播
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.05,0:04:41.13,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,黑豹车队即将到达吾野学校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:48.02,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,如果您有快递 或是需要进行购物 请及时前往
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:51.66,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:53.66,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,这不是和代先生和御糸婆婆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:56.22,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,我们俩刚刚在那边的桥上碰见了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:05:00.41,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,我记得之前 你们不是为了一个麻袋吵了一架吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.41,0:05:02.70,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,这种事情都过去了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:05.46,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,难道你正治 还没有跟吉根她和好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.46,0:05:07.44,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,欸 这倒也不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.44,0:05:09.95,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,是不是还在抱怨她做的饭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:12.03,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,她能给你做饭就不要抱怨了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.03,0:05:15.98,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,话是这么说 我是灰熊 她是赤麂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:17.70,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,我们的口味真的天差地别啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:18.88,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,口味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:20.19,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,太小家子气了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:21.54,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,我才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:23.80,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,说到底 这还不是食物的问题嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:24.93,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.93,0:05:26.99,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,在吾野变成动物不也挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:30.20,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,我还听说有些地方的人 全都变成大树了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:30.74,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,树
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:31.93,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,生长在山上的树木
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:34.32,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,变成动物后移动速度也变快了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:35.62,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.62,0:05:37.72,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,变成熊之后 我总是饿的好快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.72,0:05:40.70,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,正治你要时变成一小棵树就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:42.84,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,或者石头 蘑菇 还有铁线虫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.84,0:05:43.74,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:46.39,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,习惯之后 作为动物的生活其实也并没有多糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.39,0:05:47.91,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,这点倒确实
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:50.10,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,我都当了两年的熊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:05:51.66,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,早就习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:52.92,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,确实哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.92,0:05:56.24,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,之前淳史变成指猴 还一直都很沮丧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.53,0:05:59.36,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,原来那天晚上闲逛 我看到的是淳史啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:01.64,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,他也到这个年龄了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:05.95,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,要早知道会发生这种事 能早点离开吾野就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:07.80,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,无论走到哪里 在吾野的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:09.63,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,总会变成鸟类或是哺乳动物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.63,0:06:10.35,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.35,0:06:13.38,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,离不离开 都还照旧变成某种动物 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.38,0:06:14.26,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:16.76,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,在7G事件发生前 失踪的那个女孩还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.76,0:06:19.01,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,她现在在哪里 做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.01,0:06:21.73,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,千仓家的女孩 好像还在寻找她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:23.30,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,先不说她在不在吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:24.57,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,一人独自在陌生地带
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:27.02,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,突然变成动物 可怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.02,0:06:28.66,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,除了适应没别的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:29.94,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:33.42,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,虽然不用再为缴纳健康保险和养老金发愁了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.94,0:06:36.37,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,再者说连诊所都没剩下几个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:39.05,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,所有的官僚早就灰飞烟灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:40.96,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,如果你现在走到稻荷山公园
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:43.28,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,听说还有一个非常好的医生在那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.28,0:06:45.10,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,不过这是我听说的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:46.70,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:49.67,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,谁知道你走过去 到底要花上几年时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:52.18,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,再说你还有没有命能活着到那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:55.34,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,还有 你都不知道他们是不是人类医生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.34,0:06:57.52,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,你是说人类的医生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:59.13,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,可能是给人类看病的医生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.13,0:07:00.80,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,也可能是「人类医生」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.32,0:07:04.87,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,啊 你说它能给人看病 但却不是人类了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.87,0:07:08.02,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,他不能给人类看病 但确仍是人类对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.02,0:07:11.10,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,那个在稻荷山的医术高明的医生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.10,0:07:13.31,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,就好比是「咖喱味便便」那样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.31,0:07:14.91,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶你太恶心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:15.81,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.81,0:07:17.60,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,我只是在说「形而上」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:18.65,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,意义不明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:20.09,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,女孩们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:23.19,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,说到咖喱 是不是肚子饿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:26.15,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,一些美味的蟋蟀 我可以分给你们一点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.15,0:07:27.52,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,不用 谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.52,0:07:29.38,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,现在吃点昆虫也没啥不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:30.91,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,不要 一点也不可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:32.42,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,但听说很有营养价值
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.42,0:07:34.38,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,营养什么的才不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.38,0:07:37.29,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,大米的话一年收获六次 能吃到撑死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:39.35,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,还有苦瓜 卡路里是足够的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:41.97,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,总之可爱与浪漫才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.97,0:07:44.05,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,啊又来 逃避现实
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.05,0:07:46.45,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,难道你是超·乐观主义 做梦酱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:49.76,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,我可是 知道你想说我什么哦 小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:51.06,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,你当我笨蛋 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.06,0:07:52.37,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,对的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:53.86,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,好火大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:54.90,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,您客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.81,0:07:59.04,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,无论发生什么吵架绝对禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:00.64,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,但是小晶她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:01.54,ZH-Main-up-8-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.49,0:08:04.05,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,被骂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.05,0:08:06.50,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,被抚子姐骂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:07.86,ZH-Main-up-8-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,小晶你也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:09.57,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.57,0:08:10.36,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:12.09,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,小晶真是个乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:13.91,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲实也是好孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:15.50,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.50,0:08:16.81,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,那个 抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:19.07,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,黑豹车队来得太晚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.07,0:08:21.62,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,是啊 我们等了好久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.62,0:08:23.73,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我的小灵通收到了邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:25.78,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,说明他们应该就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.78,0:08:28.58,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,难道黑豹车队全军覆灭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.58,0:08:29.86,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,这下可糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:31.86,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,我的杂志今天应该到了的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:33.45,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留她也不在这
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:35.40,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,确实挺少见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.40,0:08:38.49,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,今天井口老师 不是要对她进行前途咨询吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:40.48,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,前途 原来是这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:42.65,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,但现在讨论这个没啥意义
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.65,0:08:44.92,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,这些难过的话就别提了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:45.70,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,没啥没啥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.70,0:08:47.77,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,这不是什么值得悲伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.77,0:08:48.81,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,而是眼前的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.81,0:08:51.33,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,啊 是善治郎先生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.33,0:08:53.06,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,吾野的标志性景观
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.06,0:08:55.30,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,他以前可是很高大英俊的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:57.72,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,两年前他回到吾野这里时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:09:00.14,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,就变成这样只会「吧吧」的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:04.85,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,善治郎特别之处 是还能保持人类模样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:07.67,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,只是普通地大了二十一岁零三个月
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:10.46,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,吾野的其他人都变成了动物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:11.74,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,噢 说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.74,0:09:12.44,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,确实如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:17.26,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,我们不久之后 也会变成某种动物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.88,0:09:18.95,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,而且还不能选择
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.43,0:09:20.59,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:21.60,ZH-Main-Down-2,Kazuyo,0,0,0,,你又哔哔了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:22.63,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:25.39,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,我真的好久没有吃肉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.39,0:09:28.01,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,果然还是肉更加好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.01,0:09:30.22,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,比起米饭 甜番薯 还有苦瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:31.90,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,那是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:33.26,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,肉真的好好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:35.46,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,吃肉真的太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.46,0:09:37.99,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,柔嫩得如血滴般稀有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.99,0:09:39.73,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,不对 超级稀有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.73,0:09:41.47,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,忍不住我真想啃几口生肉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:43.27,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,等会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:53.11,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:54.87,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你这只食欲贪婪的小熊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.17,0:09:56.74,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,诶 我刚刚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:09:58.54,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,正治先生 这样不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.54,0:10:00.47,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你完全变成熊的习性了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.47,0:10:02.27,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,诶 真的吗 别开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.27,0:10:04.12,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留你的「加课」怎么样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:05.34,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 加课
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:07.74,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 那完全问题不大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.74,0:10:09.46,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,他问了你的前途职业选择 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:11.34,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 他问我之后想要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:13.96,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我说我要「寻找她」就被说教了一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:16.54,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,「寻找她」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:33.33,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:50.75,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,抱歉 我们来迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:53.75,ZH-Main-Down-2,Masaharu,0,0,0,,高先生 别一人吃独食啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:55.24,ZH-Main-Down-2,Taka,0,0,0,,先到先得嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:57.55,ZH-Main-Down-2,Oito,0,0,0,,眼里只有吃肉没有别的 真无语
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:10:59.58,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,吾野这次又是大丰收了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:00.31,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.31,0:11:01.74,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,猫哥 怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:02.86,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,有什么消息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.86,0:11:04.96,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,没有 这次又是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.23,0:11:06.27,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.53,0:11:07.77,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,传言呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:10.29,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,比如镇上有新面孔 或是有人离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:11.61,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这些传言有没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:15.03,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,这些传言也没听过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.03,0:11:18.00,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,能够与外面交流的沟通点并不多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:21.33,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,如果有新的人出现 这种新闻肯定会马上传播
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.33,0:11:22.01,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.01,0:11:24.24,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,吾野这没有任何要报告的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:26.32,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我每天都在这里巡逻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.32,0:11:27.35,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:28.23,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,你们三人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.56,0:11:30.07,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,你们拜托的东西 我们终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:30.94,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:32.24,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,我的练马杂志
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.24,0:11:34.12,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,你不知道这是二手书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:35.54,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,咱从不奢求
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:38.08,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,现在根本没有新出版的书看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:40.09,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,诶 真的竟然找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:42.67,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,练马国的爱丽丝 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:43.86,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,这就是杂志
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.86,0:11:45.46,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,真的好怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.46,0:11:46.86,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,在7G事件之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.86,0:11:51.19,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,这个节目一直都在埼玉电视台 每周四晚12：30分放送
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:53.25,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,超现实的毒药真的太好笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:55.85,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,这也是可爱又浪漫的故事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.85,0:11:57.98,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你们说的是同一档节目吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:11:58.52,ZH-Main-Down-2,Group,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:11:59.77,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,听我说 猫哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.77,0:12:01.67,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,果然还是雇我给你们打工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.67,0:12:03.19,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,哈 不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.19,0:12:04.46,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,你说什么都不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.46,0:12:05.60,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,这很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:08.37,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,再者说我可是吾野柔术二段
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.27,0:12:13.46,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,自从7G事件之后 熊是首先倒下的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.27,0:12:17.42,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,鹈鹕 袋鼠 飞脚 也相继停业了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:21.01,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,剩下仅存的我们 虽然继续在送快递
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:22.97,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,但能坚持到什么时候也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.94,0:12:27.03,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,如果我有什么发现 肯定会告诉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.03,0:12:28.26,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,好好耐心等待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:30.51,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,就像找到那本书一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:33.06,ZH-Main-Down-2,Neko,0,0,0,,一切终将可能柳暗花明的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:34.56,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:36.57,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不要总是想靠言语糊弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.06,0:12:41.07,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,可恶 猫哥好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.27,0:12:41.52,ZH-Main-up-8-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,他们走了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:43.36,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,还要再等一个月啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:46.04,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,或者视情况等的时间会更多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.04,0:12:46.45,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:48.44,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,抚子你买了什么东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.44,0:12:49.36,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:50.45,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,啊 这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:52.13,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是香桃木花苗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.13,0:12:53.21,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,香 啥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.21,0:12:54.11,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:55.92,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是什么花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:57.09,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,现在还能生长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:13:01.38,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这里能种的只有大米 荞麦 还有苦瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:02.41,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:05.22,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但是无论如何我很想要香桃木
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:08.38,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但是 为什么我突然会想要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:09.90,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,到底会是什么原因呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:11.22,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,问我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:12.26,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,香桃木
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.87,0:13:14.44,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,啊嘞 以前确实是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:15.98,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,所以小晶你买了什么书
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:18.38,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,龙彦的「黑魔法手册」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:19.32,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,龙彦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:22.88,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,说起龙彦肯定是指涩泽龙彦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.88,0:13:24.40,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,谁会那么肯定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.42,0:13:26.95,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,怎么了 静留
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.37,0:13:29.75,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,竟然还有新出版的报纸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:32.08,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,DaiyaGate 将会进一步扩大影响
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:33.00,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,这啥意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:34.80,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,这个人 难不成就是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:35.62,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:36.98,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.98,0:13:38.35,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,哈 怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.35,0:13:40.46,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,葉香 真的是葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:42.09,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,哈 这个葉香是那个葉香吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.09,0:13:44.23,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,还有谁能叫葉香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.23,0:13:45.45,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 这什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:46.48,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,这是什么时候的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.48,0:13:47.39,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,说是上个月的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:48.23,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.23,0:13:49.30,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,完全无法相信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:51.95,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,她为什么会在池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.19,0:13:54.75,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我要告诉小雪奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:56.02,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:14:02.65,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,两年前的那一天 世界完全改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:06.56,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,火车站之间的距离 城镇之间的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.56,0:14:08.41,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,突然增加到无法跨越的长度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:09.94,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这还不单单是距离的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.94,0:14:12.96,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,人和生物都发生了彻底的改变
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.36,0:14:16.91,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,在吾野的成年人都变成了动物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:20.67,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,虽然现在 还保留有人类的常识
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:25.51,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但总可能有一天 会变成真正的动物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:29.59,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是吾野的情况 或许算是比较好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.34,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:32.43,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,小雪奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:33.01,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,快看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.06,0:14:49.82,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,最初的时候大家都被震惊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.29,0:14:52.59,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,自己变成了奇怪的动物 大吃一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.59,0:14:55.24,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,愤怒 自暴自弃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:59.75,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,一些人组成调查小组 打算离开吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:03.09,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,一半的人中途放弃折返回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:05.00,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,剩下的一半人再也没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:07.68,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,小雪奶奶 竟然哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.68,0:15:11.01,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,这可能是 她刚知道自己唯一的孙女平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:12.09,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,太高兴了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:13.30,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:15.68,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,小雪奶奶也上了年纪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:18.35,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,豚鼠的寿命 可能还剩五六年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:18.95,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.95,0:15:21.43,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,为什么小晶你要说这些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.43,0:15:23.16,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,是玲实你提到她的年龄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:24.96,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,你是真的神经大意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.96,0:15:26.93,ZH-Main-Down-2,Akira,0,0,0,,难得我好心告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:26.93,ZH-Main-up-8-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,要好好相处
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:30.55,ZH-Main-Down-2,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:32.93,ZH-Main-Down-2,Reimi,0,0,0,,给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.86,0:15:41.95,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.91,0:15:48.84,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,异变的原因 说是7G网络暴走失控所造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.46,0:15:52.63,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是 回归「本来」的方法完全无从知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.02,0:15:55.55,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,或者说 我感觉并没有人想要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:15:59.64,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,欢迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:00.43,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:02.23,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,我做好了晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:04.76,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,虽然还是一如既往的苦瓜和米饭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:06.34,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,要先加热后再吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:07.54,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:13.07,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,应该说该感谢7G还是该谴责 总之电还通着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:18.29,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,虽然无法看电视或是上网 但小灵通在近距离能用来联系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:20.70,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,冰箱虽然还在工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:23.38,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是和微波炉同时使用会跳闸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:27.46,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们不能像以前一样肆无忌惮使用电
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.97,0:16:30.41,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,甚至说这到底是不是电能 我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.89,0:16:35.26,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,像是电能通过铁轨传递能量 感觉才是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:39.47,ZH-Main-Down-2,Yoka,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:42.03,ZH-Main-Down-2,Yoka,0,0,0,,原来静留 你是这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:43.67,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.67,0:16:45.67,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什么是这样的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:47.66,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香你也是这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.97,0:16:49.11,ZH-Main-Down-2,Yoka,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:51.99,ZH-Main-Down-2,Yoka,0,0,0,,毕竟我就是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.08,0:16:53.58,ZH-Main-Down-2,Yoka,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.58,0:16:55.95,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你说什么抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.31,0:16:59.33,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我根本不知道 葉香你到底在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:02.48,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,「这种人」到底什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:05.92,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那晚之后 再也没见过葉香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.55,0:17:07.61,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,也再也没碰见过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:09.34,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,而且我也没有找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:13.63,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怪不得我找不到她 原来她在池袋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:16.16,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我以为她就在吾野附近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:18.84,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,还苦苦寻找她了两年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:20.13,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:21.35,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.86,0:17:26.60,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我说波奇 为什么你没有变成人类呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:29.39,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,既然所有人长大后都会变成动物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.39,0:17:31.73,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那波奇变成了人类不也挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:33.36,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,确实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:37.65,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,如果葉香就在附近 波奇应该也会告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.65,0:17:38.82,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,毕竟她是你的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:41.74,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我怎么从来都没有注意到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:46.19,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:47.30,ZH-Main-Down-2,Group,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.35,0:17:54.17,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,善治郎先生 你怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:56.30,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,站在这种地方可是很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:57.01,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:17:59.94,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,帽 帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:01.09,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,募集
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:05.85,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.88,0:18:09.94,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,帽子的条带
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:11.69,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,波奇 这个是什么知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:15.78,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶 你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:16.51,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶 等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:18.29,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,善治郎 那边很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:31.38,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这里面有什么东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.24,0:18:48.95,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.95,0:18:50.56,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,吧吧的帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.18,0:18:53.80,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,庞太郎那个臭小子真他妈走狗屎运
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:56.03,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,说了多少次要他放弃7G
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:57.86,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,这种计划是不可能成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:18:58.82,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:03.27,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,它能够破坏物理定律 但他却无视研究人员警告
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.27,0:19:06.28,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,只盲目接受「牟利者」提供的不可靠信息
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:09.38,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,在最坏的情况下没有放弃 反而招来了最不愿发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.38,0:19:10.68,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,草泥马的婊子跟谁过不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.68,0:19:12.30,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,为了不让我打扰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.30,0:19:14.45,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,用软绵绵手术让我变得软绵绵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.45,0:19:16.75,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,完全无法控制 简直凶残到毫无人性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:18.55,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,所以你给我等着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:20.50,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,我绝对要把7G停给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.50,0:19:22.87,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,不会让你霸占池袋的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:24.43,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,等会 你说池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:25.16,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,对的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:26.89,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,我不能就这样离开池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:28.17,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,我要马上去阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.17,0:19:31.31,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,迫不得已 我善治郎这局身躯将搭乘这两千序列
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.55,0:19:32.96,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,不对 等会 这是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:36.57,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,你是 千仓静留对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:38.42,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,你小的时候跌到泥沟里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.42,0:19:39.32,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怎样都行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.53,0:19:41.86,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,重要的是你是如何把两千系列开过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:43.49,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你会开火车吗 善治郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:46.19,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,你说我会不会开火车
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.19,0:19:46.91,ZH-Main-Down-2,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.81,0:19:51.46,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:52.11,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,咋了咋了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.11,0:19:53.37,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,给我再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:55.95,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.95,0:19:57.17,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,再来一次
