Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:03.39,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,到底什么鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.39,0:20:06.52,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,帽子不是能把他变回去吗 不对嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.52,0:20:07.93,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,喂 你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.81,0:20:09.56,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.46,0:20:11.93,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,无论如何 都要确保自身安全
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:13.77,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,谢谢你 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:15.19,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我出发了
