Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.08,0:20:21.28,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru's Mother,0,0,0,,记得叫他别做傻事 快点回家里来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.52,0:20:22.20,ZH-Main-Down-2,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我明白了
